│ ╭─ Hosts ────────────────────────────────────────────╮   ││                                      │
│ │                                                    │   ││                                      │
│ │   It's quiet in here.                              │   ││                                      │
│ │                                                    │   ││                                      │
│ │   purple reads hosts from ~/.ssh/config and from   │   ││                                      │
│ │   the cloud providers you connect. Add one by hand │   ││                                      │
│ │   or sync a provider and the list fills up.        │   ││                                      │
│ │                                                    │   ││                                      │
│ │   a  add a host                                    │   ││                                      │
│ │   S  open providers to sync from the cloud         │   ││                                      │
│ │                                                    │   ││                                      │
